title: Old Town Road (Small Town Traffic Soundscape)
description:
On this bonus episode of Sleep & Relax ASMR, we visit an old town road in Georgia and listen to the quiet street soundscape featuring cars and buses passing by. This is a binaural recording. Enjoy!
